{"tid":1558884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[柒出國際] 支那干擾葡國一個同香港有關嘅宗教政治會議","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T00:17:50.000Z","uid":97997,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2456574eadb03c2e7ad5f4ee11e73997f7d84ae6","tid":1558884,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"05.09.2019 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那大使館職員意圖干擾一個在花地馬，有宗教領袖與政治領袖出席的會議，因為該會議有來自香港的主教。支那大使館職員意圖阻止來自香港的主教和另外兩個賓客發言。<br />\n<br />\n該會議名為 International Network of Catholic Lawmakers，出席人士包括白宮幕僚長 Mick Mulvaney 和 匈牙利總理 Viktor Orb&aacute;n。<br />\n<br />\n支那大使館職員意圖拍攝參加者、嘗試進入會議、了解會議內容，甚至跟蹤到聖母瑪利亞教堂（Basilica da Nossa Senhora do Ros&aacute;rio）的祈禱活動。<br />\n<br />\n葡國外長已經確認有支那官員出現在花地馬，並正調查。總統 Marcelo Rebelo de Sousa 也已經得自此事。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.sabado.pt/portugal/detalhe/espioes-chineses-apanhados-em-fatima\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sabado.pt%2Fportugal%2Fdetalhe%2Fespioes-chineses-apanhados-em-fatima&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4UuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=679a2855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sabado.pt/portugal/detalhe/espioes-chineses-apanhados-em-fatima</a>"},{"pid":"41cc38e87d7691978f75a957dc8e369f522ba246","tid":1558884,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"10個自稱支那註里斯本領事館職員，嘗試在花地瑪，跟蹤參加一個宗教與政治領袖會議（22-25/8）的陳日君樞機<br />\n<br />\n該10蝗團隊用了一個星期，監察和追問相關人士，而87歲的陳日君樞機為支那正苦 top 10 敵人。<br />\n<br />\n該10人團隊沒有成功隱藏行為，葡國政府發現了其行徑，不排除他們是間諜。儘管其差劣的行徑，他們並沒有觸犯法例。<br />\n<br />\n外相 Augusto Santos Silva 確認正調查有否違反法例，總統 Marcelo Rebelo Sousa已經得悉此事。<br />\n<br />\n此會議邀請了200個宗教和政治領袖，有兩個香港代表出席，匈牙利首相 Viktor Orb&aacute;n 和白宮幕僚長也有出席。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://executivedigest.sapo.pt/espioes-chineses-apanhados-em-fatima/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexecutivedigest.sapo.pt%2Fespioes-chineses-apanhados-em-fatima%2F&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4UuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=0190e592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://executivedigest.sapo.pt/espioes-chineses-apanhados-em-fatima/</a>"},{"pid":"4563fd0ea90c55b149c068fceea4a53e043c6da6","tid":1558884,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"[911恐襲] 除左瘋狂Twitter，仲有樣 好 撚 重 要 既野要一齊做！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558812</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e31e6bbe6e78b100e2015dcb494edf5f771ede09","tid":1558884,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:16:01.000Z","msg":"共狗罰行必須推"},{"pid":"a13e1743e7e538deccafec085a11d5d30dc1cb41","tid":1558884,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0815c0150db8f4f548a1d6f47d205f7b247d85bd","tid":1558884,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:22:39.000Z","msg":"Levantai hoje de novo<br />\nO esplendor de Portugal!<br />\n<img src=\"https://buccaneersreef.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Portuguese-Carrack-1585-Wheatley.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuccaneersreef.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F01%2FPortuguese-Carrack-1585-Wheatley.jpg&h=1c0f2fd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f02a351ee8ac3eef84a4ec20a2a75a5b1792b7c","tid":1558884,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"根本就係世界毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d41a3284a1cfc19d21ecc2125568240be3089e","tid":1558884,"uid":78873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0815c0150db8f4f548a1d6f47d205f7b247d85bd","tid":1558884,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:22:39.000Z","msg":"Levantai hoje de novo<br />\nO esplendor de Portugal!<br />\n<img src=\"https://buccaneersreef.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Portuguese-Carrack-1585-Wheatley.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuccaneersreef.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F01%2FPortuguese-Carrack-1585-Wheatley.jpg&h=1c0f2fd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那 南海自古以來也是葡國的"},{"pid":"b919a1f0467907a34d4bfd4c389286f3a0e6002c","tid":1558884,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:12:45.000Z","msg":"上咗蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中方阻赴葡講解反送中 陳日君轟野蠻：以為自己係世界主人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54b10b140317e6fa2b6bd7842f944020ae78f5aa","tid":1558884,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那食屎啦"}]}